Commitment Letter
This commitment letter is made between Net Verse Hotel, represented by Mr. Mohammad Amin Ahmadi, and the Guest.
The Guest of Net Verse Hotel commits to adhering to the following terms during their stay at Net Verse Hotel:
1. Damage to Hotel Property : - In the event of any damage caused to the hotel’s property and belongings, the guest commits to fully compensating for the damages and paying the related costs upon check-out.
2. Check-in and Check-out Dates : - The guest commits to arriving at the hotel and vacating the room precisely on the specified check-in and check-out dates. Otherwise, the hotel holds no responsibility for any delays or potential issues.
3. Adherence to Hotel Rules and Regulations : - The guest commits to following all hotel rules and regulations during their stay. Failure to comply with the rules will result in serious action by the hotel.
This commitment letter becomes effective upon your acceptance.
